Description:
Introducing the legendary Triple X frame on a diet – meet the 3X4 110/100 - 12.8 Titanium Pink frame from POWERSLIDE, one of the fastest and most capable inline race frames available. This exceptional frame is the result of collaboration between our engineers, designers, and professional race team members led by Gaby Rueda. The 3X4 110/100 frame is incredibly lightweight at just 155g, without compromising performance. Constructed from high-quality aircraft aluminum and CNC-machined to perfection, this strong, stiff frame meets the demands of the world's top inline racers, ensuring superb power transfer with every stride. Designed with the trusted 195mm mounting system, the Triple X 110/100 - 12.8 Titanium Pink frame is built for speed and can accommodate a Hi-lo setup with 3x110mm and 1x100mm wheels

