FR FRX 80 White Freerdie Skate

&nbsp;

Experience superior control and a smooth ride with these skates. Featuring lowered X3R rockerable 243mm frames, fast Downtown 80mm/85A wheels, and high-performance FR Twincam MW7 Freeride bearings, you'll enjoy responsive handling and effortless gliding. The High Stability Hard Shell, secure Safety Top Buckle, and supportive Wide Powerstrap keep you locked in, while the removable FR Comfort liner ensures all-day comfort.
